// BT-2212: owner class for the synthetic String extensions registered in
// system_navigation_extensions_test. It only needs to be a loaded class whose
// name resolves to a class object via `resolveExtensionClass:`, so that
// `extendersOf:` can return the owner as a class object. No state — `Object
// subclass:` forbids data declarations.

Object subclass: SysnavFixtureExtender

  sysnavFixtureExtenderMarker => 0
